'''Docking Bay 71''' was one of [[Skagras]] [[City/Legends|city's]] [[Hangar/Legends|docking bays]]. It was here that [[Dannen Lifehold]] was attacked by [[Chokk (Bloxian)|Chokk]] and [[Bakk]], while doing a smuggling job for [[Linkaas]].

